text: "Bennie and the Jets" (also titled "Benny & the Jets") is a 1974 song by Elton John and is the third single from his seventh studio album Goodbye Yellow Brick Road (1973). It topped the single charts in Canada and the United States. It went to number 5 in Australia, number 13 in New Zealand, number 18 in Ireland and number 37 in the United Kingdom. == References == Category:1974 songs Category:Elton John songs
